me.bhop.bjdautilities.command.annotation

Annotation Type Usage


  • @Target(value=METHOD)
 @Retention(value=RUNTIME)
public @interface Usage
    An override for the default command usage. This is not required for any command (parent or child), however it can be included on either one of them to override the default generated usage for something customized.
